PHP Extension: PHP Interface to IDAM

Based on C++:  http://www.php-cpp.com 

Basic extension: http://www.php-cpp.com/documentation/your-first-extension

Requirements:

1> PHP native interaction with the IDAM/Provenance database
2> PHP native interaction with the Pin Board database
3> PHP Extension library to IDAM
4> PHP interaction through the IDAM extension to backend IDAM server plugin

Postgres needs a php extension: pgsql.so
libpgsql.so also needs to be on the search path
php.ini needs extension=pgsql.so uncommented 
